entries.journal_entry_description: Bring Cal Handro in to Officer M'kae.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Go to the safehouse and talk to the head guard.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: You have been attacked by mercenaries, hired by the rebels.  Kill them!
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: You have been attacked by the ranking officer.  Kill him.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Now that you survived the attack, talk to the Head Guard again.
entries.task04_journal_entry_title: Talk to the Head Guard Again
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: It seems that Wolff Kalos was also interested in acquiring Cal.  Get information from him one way or another.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Return to Officer M'Kae and learn if there is something that you can do about Wolff Kalos.
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Kill General Garax Hadriin and get his computer codes
entries.task08_journal_entry_description: Use the main computer terminal to download Wolff Kalos' personal information to find a weakness.
entries.task09_journal_entry_description: Return to Wolff Kalos and encourage him to cooperate.
entries.task10_journal_entry_description: You know where Cal Handro is. Go into space and shoot him down before he can further damage the Alliance.  Return to Officer M'kae when you have won.
entries.task11_journal_entry_description: You have been rewarded for a job well done.
entries.task12_journal_entry_description: You know where Cal Handro is. Go into space and shoot him down before he can further damage the Alliance.  Return to Officer M'kae when you have won.
entries.task13_journal_entry_description: You have been rewarded for a job well done.
